tempting tropicals is a horticultural tour de force ... tempting tropicals is a horticultural tour de force , packed with detailed information about growth habits , propagation tips , and the soil , temperature and light requirements of more than eight score tropical plants . the fascinating , well written text is ornamented with full color photographs of these exotic beauties that marvelously display each plant 's unique attributes . the superb text and photos are presented with the exacting production values that the publisher is well known for in the gardening community . this book is a must for all real phytophiles